---
layout: layouts/docs.njk
title: Fixture Realism Checklist
section: quality
---

{% from "partials/tag.njk" import tag %}

{% set completed = items | selectattr("done") | list | length %}

<section class="hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">Quality pass</p>
  <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
  <p>Keep sample files believable enough that manual UI review is based on realistic code and docs.</p>
  <p>{{ completed }} of {{ items | length }} checklist items completed.</p>
</section>

<section class="content-grid">
  <article>
    <h2>Review focus</h2>
    <ul class="bullet-list">
      {% for focus in review_focus %}
      <li>{{ focus }}</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>

    <h2>Checklist</h2>
    <ol class="checklist">
      {% for item in items %}
      <li class="checklist__item">
        {{ tag(item.done and "done" or "pending") }}
        <strong>{{ item.label }}</strong>
        {% if item.detail %}<p>{{ item.detail }}</p>{% endif %}
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>

    <h2>Useful commands</h2>
    <pre><code>pnpm --dir web exec tsc --noEmit
pnpm -s web:build
rg -n "metric[0-9]{2}|entry_[0-9]{3}" D:/xdnote/GitCodeViewer</code></pre>

    <h2>Editorial rule</h2>
    <p>If a file reads like generated filler, rewrite it around a concrete artifact such as a config, guide, diagram, report, or build file.</p>
  </article>

  <aside>
    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Alias coverage</h3>
      <ul>
        {% for alias in aliases %}
        <li><code>.{{ alias.ext }}</code> -> {{ alias.language }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Current blockers</h3>
      {% if blockers.length %}
      <ul>
        {% for blocker in blockers %}
        <li>{{ blocker }}</li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
      {% else %}
      <p>No active blockers.</p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Why this matters</h3>
      <p>Reviewers make layout decisions from these samples, so unrealistic content leads to unrealistic UI judgments.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="panel">
      <h3>Notes</h3>
      <p>Legacy modes without fold support should render full-width code blocks.</p>
      <p>Phone title affordance should remain subtle and should not leak into tablet layouts.</p>
    </div>
  </aside>
</section>
